# Maugood backup cron (v1.0 P24).
# supercronic crontab — see ops/backup/Dockerfile.
#
# Five fields: m h dom mon dow. The container's TZ is set to
# Asia/Muscat by default (override via ``TZ=...`` on the
# service definition); 0 2 * * * therefore fires at 02:00
# Muscat local time, which is what BRD §"backups" asks for.

0 2 * * * /app/scripts/backup.sh
